You might even have lost your life,

253
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:53,060
Aren't you here to save me?

254
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:03,580
I didn't expect that Qu Zhizhan

255
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:05,220
would actually go so far as to
incite a rebellion,

256
00:15:06,220 --> 00:15:08,740
He is so reckless, It's beyond my expectations,

257
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:13,140
Rest assured, I already have a solution,

258
00:15:13,940 --> 00:15:15,300
I will surely not disappoint them,

259
00:15:17,860 --> 00:15:19,820
Even if you solved this tax problem,

260
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:21,740
As long as the Grand Princess

261
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:23,940
still holds the wife and children
of Qu Chongyu,

262
00:15:23,940 --> 00:15:26,940
Then Qu Zhizhan will not cease
his intention to kill us,

263
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:30,940
Shouyue, I want to return to Chang'an,

264
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:35,500
Although I am not completely sure that
I will succeed,

265
00:15:36,020 --> 00:15:37,820
I think it's worth taking a gamble,

266
00:15:38,740 --> 00:15:40,700
That is our only chance to turn the tables,

267
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:43,640
My foster father and Empress Wu
are in Chang'an,

268
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,060
I will not be in danger,

269
00:16:04,832 --> 00:16:05,900
Today, Protector-General made the order to

270
00:16:05,900 --> 00:16:07,580
withdraw all the guards outside the courtyard,

271
00:16:07,580 --> 00:16:09,100
After that, the public went to make trouble,

272
00:16:09,100 --> 00:16:10,360
Madam Kudi got hurt,

273
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,700
Also, I just saw many officers in the yard,

274
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:27,520
Minister,

275
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:29,840
What does this mean?

276
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:31,780
We are here to guard
under the command of Protector-General,

277
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:36,820
Minister, the people in the city
are rebelling right now,

278
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:38,780
It may be dangerous to go out at this time,

279
00:16:38,780 --> 00:16:40,704
Please stay in the workshop for now,

280
00:16:40,704 --> 00:16:41,728
Stand aside,

281
00:16:41,728 --> 00:16:43,900
Protector-General
has strict orders not to let you leave,

282
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:46,740
Otherwise, our lives would be in danger,

283
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:48,220
Please understand, Minister,

284
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:51,100
Let go or I'm going to kill you now,

285
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:55,060
If Minister kills me, only one of us will die,

286
00:16:55,700 --> 00:16:57,140
If I let you out today,

287
00:16:57,740 --> 00:16:59,488
then my entire family will be dead,

288
00:16:59,488 --> 00:17:00,580
Fine, then…

289
00:17:00,580 --> 00:17:01,940
- Minister!
- I will kill you,

290
00:17:01,940 --> 00:17:03,220
If I were to stop you,

291
00:17:04,340 --> 00:17:07,100
would you also have to kill me then?

292
00:17:13,980 --> 00:17:17,980
Chongyu, you'll have to endure a few days
in the workshop first,

293
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:20,820
Wait until things settle down outside,

294
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:23,260
Then you can go wherever you like,

295
00:17:23,780 --> 00:17:25,180
I won't interfere with you at all,

296
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:26,820
Father, are you hiding something from me?

297
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:30,580
What could I possibly be hiding from you?

298
00:17:30,580 --> 00:17:32,100
I won't let you go out,

299
00:17:33,100 --> 00:17:36,240
I am truly concerned for your safety,

300
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:38,380
You are my only son,

301
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:40,520
If anything were to happen to you,

302
00:17:40,520 --> 00:17:43,540
how could I go on living afterwards?

303
00:17:44,620 --> 00:17:46,220
What if I insist on going out?

304
00:18:11,140 --> 00:18:13,900
Father, Pei Xingjian's visit
to Xizhou this time

305
00:18:14,900 --> 00:18:16,220
is definitely not as simple as it seems,

306
00:18:16,820 --> 00:18:18,540
If you persist on killing him,

307
00:18:18,540 --> 00:18:20,440
I'm afraid this will bring disaster
to the Qu family,

308
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:23,552
If I don't kill him, that will bring disaster
to the Qu family,

309
00:18:23,552 --> 00:18:24,640
Father,

310
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:26,460
I know what you're worried about,

311
00:18:26,460 --> 00:18:29,300
Although I'm old, I'm not senile yet,

312
00:18:29,860 --> 00:18:33,300
Protector-General, something bad has happened

313
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:36,100
What happened?

314
00:18:36,100 --> 00:18:39,800
For some reason, Madam Qu and Prefect Wang
started arguing,

315
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:42,580
Madam Qu is now threatening to hang herself,

316
00:18:51,540 --> 00:18:53,620
Lady Jing, what are you
messing around with again?

317
00:18:58,500 --> 00:19:01,312
Where is Lady Jing? Why are you here?

318
00:19:02,180 --> 00:19:04,224
Protector-General, Minister,

319
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:09,260
I'm asking you, where is Lady Jing?

320
00:19:11,968 --> 00:19:13,020
Someone come!

321
00:19:13,020 --> 00:19:14,048
No need to shout,

322
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:16,860
Lady Jing has sent the guard away,

323
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:19,300
No one will come to disturb us in a short time,

324
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:29,700
Father, brother, Liuli and Senior Official Pei

325
00:19:29,700 --> 00:19:31,140
are not here to harm our Qu family,

326
00:19:31,140 --> 00:19:33,220
I reckon there must be misunderstandings
between you guys,

327
00:19:33,220 --> 00:19:34,880
Let's have a deep discussion tonight,

328
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:38,620
Lady Jing, what are you trying to do?
Open the door!

329
00:19:38,620 --> 00:19:40,660
Stop shouting, your loud voice is of no use,

330
00:19:41,340 --> 00:19:43,700
I did this completely for our Qu family,

331
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:46,680
Stay calm and have a good chat
with Senior Official Pei,

332
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:49,020
Once you have settled your details,
I will open the door,

333
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:53,180
Stop messing around, open the door for me!

334
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:56,600
Madam, locking me up is one thing,

335
00:19:56,600 --> 00:19:59,340
Isn't it inappropriate
to treat the Protector-General like this?

336
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:00,800
If I don't lock them inside,

337
00:20:00,800 --> 00:20:02,020
can they have a proper conversation?

338
00:20:03,100 --> 00:20:04,740
Have you forgotten that
you asked me to help them?

339
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:08,100
Wang Junmeng, I've heard your voice,

340
00:20:08,940 --> 00:20:10,980
Hurry up and open the door for me,
did you hear that!

341
00:20:11,540 --> 00:20:13,120
- I'm coming,
- Come over here,

342
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:14,740
