343
00:20:15,340 --> 00:20:16,380
Look at yourself,

344
00:20:17,100 --> 00:20:20,020
But madam, madam, you…

345
00:20:20,020 --> 00:20:21,420
- Protector-General…
- Will you leave or not?

346
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:24,740
Protector-General, I'll come and open
the door for you in a moment,

347
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:28,140
Lady Jing, Lady Jing, come back to me!

348
00:20:28,140 --> 00:20:29,380
Hurry and open the door!

349
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:43,620
Don't think that just because
you've persuaded Lady Jing,

350
00:20:43,620 --> 00:20:45,260
you can live in peace,

351
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:47,660
This is Xizhou,

352
00:20:48,260 --> 00:20:49,940
Even if you have taken me hostage,
it doesn't change anything,

353
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:51,820
It still won't change anything,

354
00:20:52,580 --> 00:20:56,300
Protector-General, you are mistaken,
We have no malicious intent in visiting,

355
00:20:56,940 --> 00:20:58,140
No malicious intent?

356
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:05,700
Ever since you arrived in Xizhou,

357
00:21:06,620 --> 00:21:09,500
I've tried to kill you several times,

358
00:21:10,220 --> 00:21:14,080
Now, you're all aware of this
and still had the audacity to come,

359
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:17,100
And you dare to say you bear me no harm?

360
00:21:17,940 --> 00:21:19,920
We are aware of what you've done

361
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,620
is not your true intention,

362
00:21:22,340 --> 00:21:24,620
You are being threatened
and have no choice but to comply,

363
00:21:25,540 --> 00:21:26,540
So, I think,

364
00:21:27,060 --> 00:21:29,060
we can have an honest discussion,

365
00:21:33,740 --> 00:21:35,140
Who exactly is threatening you?

366
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:39,500
Who exactly is forcing you?

367
00:21:40,460 --> 00:21:42,660
And who is holding the leverage
over our Qu family?

368
00:21:43,980 --> 00:21:46,660
Making you take desperate risks,
even instigating a rebellion,

369
00:21:46,660 --> 00:21:48,540
And intending to put Pei Xingjian
in a deadly situation,

370
00:21:53,580 --> 00:21:54,656
Father,

371
00:21:58,860 --> 00:21:59,936
Father,

372
00:22:15,220 --> 00:22:16,780
It's the eldest Princess Linhai,

373
00:22:24,940 --> 00:22:28,736
She uses the lives of Fuxian and Song'er
to coerce me,

374
00:22:34,432 --> 00:22:36,420
She wants me to eliminate the Pei family,

375
00:22:48,580 --> 00:22:52,780
Lady Jing, Qu Jingtang, open the door!

376
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:57,260
Lady Jing, Wang Junmeng!

377
00:22:58,140 --> 00:22:59,820
Believe it or not, if you don't open the door,
I'll kill you!

378
00:23:04,380 --> 00:23:06,080
Chongyu!

379
00:23:06,656 --> 00:23:07,660
What are you going to do?

380
00:23:07,660 --> 00:23:09,100
Return to Chang'an,

381
00:23:09,100 --> 00:23:10,940
What's the use of going back to Chang'an now?

382
00:23:10,940 --> 00:23:12,880
Why didn't you tell me about this?

383
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:14,440
I knew you would do this,

384
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:15,620
How would I dare to tell you?

385
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,260
Do you think by not telling me,

386
00:23:17,260 --> 00:23:19,120
this matter could be kept secret forever?

387
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:21,420
Even if I told you, what could you do?

388
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:23,580
Are you going to break into
the Hedong Duke's Mansion?

389
00:23:23,580 --> 00:23:26,060
Or just kill Linhai?

390
00:23:29,300 --> 00:23:31,500
She is the esteemed Eldest Princess,

391
00:23:31,500 --> 00:23:33,380
She's the emperor's own aunt!

392
00:23:33,380 --> 00:23:35,500
If she doesn't hand over the person to me,

393
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:36,920
I don't care who she is,

394
00:23:36,920 --> 00:23:41,900
Rebel, do you intend to destroy
the entire Qu family?

395
00:23:48,900 --> 00:23:50,860
If I have a way to save both mother and child,

396
00:23:52,140 --> 00:23:53,980
Would the two of you be willing
to speak with us?

397
00:24:33,100 --> 00:24:35,900
Don't know where the Madam's confidence
comes from?

398
00:24:35,900 --> 00:24:37,700
What method will you use

399
00:24:38,300 --> 00:24:41,300
to let that arrogant and stubborn princess
submit obediently?

400
00:24:42,780 --> 00:24:44,740
I am not doubting you, Madam,

401
00:24:44,740 --> 00:24:48,540
Just that it's about the life of
my daughter-in-law and grandchild,

402
00:24:50,620 --> 00:24:52,660
It's better to ask clearly,

403
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:58,540
Protector-General should know
my relationship with Empress Wu,

404
00:24:59,100 --> 00:25:01,600
If Empress Wu puts pressure on
Hedong Duke's Mansion,

405
00:25:01,600 --> 00:25:05,180
Do you think the eldest princess still dares
to forcibly detain people?

406
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:10,180
The deep sisterly bond between
Empress Wu and Madam,

407
00:25:11,140 --> 00:25:12,900
Of course, I am aware of it,

408
00:25:14,620 --> 00:25:19,820
But why Senior Official Pei was punished
is known to everyone,

409
00:25:20,460 --> 00:25:24,000
May I ask, on what grounds does Empress Wu

410
00:25:24,000 --> 00:25:26,700
help someone who opposes her?

411
00:25:27,340 --> 00:25:31,560
Being punished is nothing more than a play
Shouyue performed with His Majesty,

412
00:25:31,560 --> 00:25:33,980
Isn't Protector-General aware of this?

413
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:38,660
But Senior Official Pei

414
00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:42,340
opposed to making Wu as the Empress,

415
00:25:42,860 --> 00:25:44,620
This is an indisputable fact,

416
00:25:45,820 --> 00:25:46,912
Senior Official Pei,

417
00:25:49,660 --> 00:25:53,380
'National calamities inevitably
begin from here',

418
00:25:54,300 --> 00:25:58,900
Presumably, those were words
from Senior Official's heart,

419
00:26:06,620 --> 00:26:09,180
Today, I am going to tell you the truth,

420
00:26:09,740 --> 00:26:12,300
I can give you a few more days to live,

421
00:26:13,020 --> 00:26:16,260
What you have said today cannot convince me,

422
00:26:16,260 --> 00:26:19,520
For the honor and disgrace of my Qu family,
I can do anything,

423
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:22,460
The Senior Official will continue to collect
grain and taxes tomorrow,

424
00:26:23,260 --> 00:26:27,100
We'll discuss further once you have
another good plan, alright?

425
00:26:49,108 --> 00:26:52,544
<i>[Pei's Mansion]</i>

426
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:15,940
When you go to Wucheng tomorrow,
wear more clothes, and also--

427
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:19,060
No worries, I will take good care of myself,

428
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:23,820
As for you, without me by your side,

429
00:27:50,131 --> 00:27:57,056
<i>[Yong'an Bridge]</i>

430
00:27:58,260 --> 00:28:01,760
Third brother, about tomorrow's matter,
what do you suggest we do?

431
00:28:01,760 --> 00:28:04,400
Let's not talk much about that Wucheng village,

432
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:07,300
