are known to be quite fierce,

433
00:28:07,300 --> 00:28:08,500
I'm worried about potential accidents,

434
00:28:10,180 --> 00:28:13,340
I'm certain that the tax payment tomorrow
will cause public grievances,

435
00:28:14,660 --> 00:28:15,840
Isn't that the truth?

436
00:28:16,980 --> 00:28:18,100
Then I will protect the Senior Official,

437
00:28:18,700 --> 00:28:20,660
Number Four and Five, both of you follow me,

438
00:28:23,060 --> 00:28:25,640
Wucheng village is about half an hour
away from Xizhou,

439
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,540
Shangxian village is quite close to Xizhou,

440
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:30,420
Rest of you stay in Xizhou to protect Madam,

441
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,780
To prevent people from Shangxian village
from causing trouble,

442
00:28:32,820 --> 00:28:33,824
What do you all think?

443
00:28:35,360 --> 00:28:38,700
Right, wouldn't doing so be foolproof?

444
00:28:47,380 --> 00:28:54,016
<i>[Wucheng Village]</i>

445
00:28:57,100 --> 00:28:59,200
I heard that Zhang Huaiji, the Advisor,
were injured from a fall off their horse,

446
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:01,660
Today, Senior Official Pei will personally
come to take it over,

447
00:29:02,624 --> 00:29:03,700
There's such a thing too?

448
00:29:03,700 --> 00:29:04,768
Not so good,

449
00:29:05,620 --> 00:29:08,020
There's a rumor that Zhang Advisor

450
00:29:08,020 --> 00:29:09,380
fell from the horse on purpose,

451
00:29:09,380 --> 00:29:11,620
Just want to avoid this trouble,

452
00:29:11,620 --> 00:29:14,240
Isn't this cutting off our last bit of hope?

453
00:29:14,240 --> 00:29:17,120
That Senior Official Pei is an official
sent by the government,

454
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:18,580
To keep his official hat,

455
00:29:19,220 --> 00:29:20,620
he wouldn't care about our life or death,

456
00:29:20,620 --> 00:29:22,220
The current situation is unexpectedly severe,

457
00:29:23,140 --> 00:29:24,820
If this group of people really
quarrel intensively,

458
00:29:25,380 --> 00:29:27,340
Senior Official Pei might have a hard time
getting away unscathed,

459
00:29:28,100 --> 00:29:29,820
If you ask me, the law don't punish the masses,

460
00:29:29,820 --> 00:29:31,700
At any rate, we are at the point of
smashing the pot to sell the iron

461
00:29:31,700 --> 00:29:32,820
and still can't make up for the taxes owed,

462
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:35,220
Could it be that they want to put everyone

463
00:29:35,220 --> 00:29:36,840
- into the jail?
- If it continues on this path,

464
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:38,180
the Senior Official's Madam…

465
00:29:40,340 --> 00:29:42,200
You must protect Senior Official Pei now,

466
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,260
I'll return to Senior Official's mansion first,

467
00:29:43,900 --> 00:29:45,340
Since no one will speak for us,

468
00:29:45,340 --> 00:29:46,432
then we will fight it out with them,

469
00:29:46,432 --> 00:29:47,520
Exactly, exactly,

470
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:49,248
Then we should also fight for our families,

471
00:29:49,248 --> 00:29:50,460
Let's give it our all!

472
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:52,580
Right, right, fight, fight, fight!

473
00:29:52,580 --> 00:29:54,300
Fight, fight, fight!

474
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:55,392
Fight, fight!

475
00:30:08,460 --> 00:30:10,460
Let's go, let's wait for them in Wucheng,

476
00:30:10,460 --> 00:30:11,960
If it comes to it, we'll fight them together,

477
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:15,220
Right, let's go, fight with them,

478
00:30:32,900 --> 00:30:34,900
Today, all homeowners should go to Wucheng
to obey orders,

479
00:30:34,900 --> 00:30:36,000
Why have so many people come?

480
00:30:36,980 --> 00:30:39,300
If your father and brothers
go to Wucheng today,

481
00:30:39,980 --> 00:30:42,400
Facing the evil one, how can you not worry?

482
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:43,640
Can't you not come out and take a look?

483
00:30:43,640 --> 00:30:45,320
Senior Official Pei is not some evil one,

484
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:47,540
