486
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:50,820
Today, if you talk to him nicely,

487
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:52,160
Make him understand everyone's hardship,

488
00:30:52,160 --> 00:30:53,620
I think he will also be reasonable,

489
00:31:37,140 --> 00:31:39,300
Senior Official Pei
has already left for Wucheng,

490
00:31:39,900 --> 00:31:42,440
