Otherwise, your subordinate--

524
00:36:13,540 --> 00:36:15,740
If I inadvertently arouse
public anger in a while,

525
00:36:16,540 --> 00:36:17,664
In this state,

526
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:19,940
