to collect overdue rent,

529
00:36:30,740 --> 00:36:31,820
He even threatened that,

530
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:35,280
those who can't pay back the overdue rent
will offset the loan with their property,

531
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:36,820
What, the property?

532
00:36:40,980 --> 00:36:43,180
Everyone, listen to me,

533
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:45,940
I believe everyone is the same as me,

534
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:48,340
We all are poor families from
Shangxian village,

535
00:36:49,580 --> 00:36:52,540
From today onwards, we will lose our homes,

536
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:55,660
fields, and all our belongings,

537
00:36:56,660 --> 00:36:59,800
We have no other choice but to become refugees,

538
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:01,500
